
ABOUT
=====
The current version of the project can be used to convert the Kinect's
disparity map to point cloud and visualize it using OpenSceneGraph. The point
cloud can be saved as PLY file.


TO COMPILE
==========
The requirements are:
- openscenegraph
- libfreenect 
- AntTweakBar

